snippet.title: Nukes
snippet.description:
Alright whats goin on guys ? its Nukes ! Welcome to my channel ! Here you will find a variety of games as i dont like to stick to one game. Anywayz you will find mainly GTA 5 on my channel and im always down for suggestions for games to play and series ideas aswell as lets play suggestions ! Alot of great content here My dudes, so make sure to check it all out and ill see you peoples later, PEACE !


PC Specs :
AMD Ryzen 7 3700x 
16GB (2 x 8GB) DDR4 3000 
Nvidia RTX 2080 Super EVGA 8GB
SanDisk - Ultra II 480GB SSD
